    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 2 • Talking about financial issues",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Juan and Diane work in the finance department of Delicious Delights, a company that makes snack foods. Here, they’re discussing the financial projections for a new product line."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Juan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I’m really excited about the launch of our new line of fat-free Delicious Delight donuts."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Diane:  "
            },
            {
              "text": "Me too. But before we go any further, we’d better make sure this product line is going to be profitable. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Juan:  "
            },
            {
              "text": "I did some. "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "back-of-the-envelope calculations"
            },
            {
              "text": " Take a look. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Diane: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I see you’ve estimated $2 million for the new equipment. Where did you get that figure? "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Juan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "That’s an "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "educated guess"
            },
            {
              "text": " based on some equipment I bought last year. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Diane: "
            },
            {
              "text": "You’re going to need to double-check that. Using old estimates can get us "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "in hot water"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Juan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "No problem. I’ll get on the phone with the manufacturer in Dallas and get a price quote. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Diane: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Do you have a sense for market demand? We should get the forecasts from the marketing department before we "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "crunch the numbers"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Juan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We don’t have those yet. Mary from marketing said maybe we’d have them next week. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Diane: "
            },
            {
              "text": "It just "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "blows my mind"
            },
            {
              "text":	" when marketing people want us to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"run numbers"
            },
            {
              "text":	" and they don’t bring us the information we need!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Juan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "If we end up "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "in the red"
            },
            {
              "text":	" on this project, it’s going to be their "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"heads on the chopping block"
            },
            {
              "text":	", not ours. They’re the ones with P&L* responsibility!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Diane: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Our CFO** won’t "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "give this project the green light"
            },
            {
              "text":	" until he sees all the numbers. If it doesn’t look like we’ll make money or at least "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"break even"
            },
            {
              "text":	", he’ll "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"pull the plug"
            },
            {
              "text":	" on the project."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
